    <img class="header-image" alt="INTO UEA student support" src="/images/ImagesINTO/UEA/Support/INTO-UEA-student-support.jpg?w=1255&q=80">
        <div class="caption_holder">
            <h1>INTO东英吉利大学的学生支持服务</h1>
        </div>
</div>
